.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Parameters
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBvoid\fP – no arguments
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Description
.sp
Some libraries \fIcough*libclang*\fP need explicit cleanup calls
at the end of program execution, even if you’ve never called
any of their functions.
.sp
